Average high concentrations in or off the coast of Pinellas have been reported over the past week. Outside the coast of Hillsborough low to high concentrations, background concentrations to high concentrations in Manatee, background concentrations to high concentrations in or off the coast of Sarasota, background concentrations to medium concentrations in or off the coast in Lee, and low concentrations in Collier.
